attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a piece of furniture. He screws the side bars and the base frame together, and then he attaches the legs. The student puts the bottom tray in place and then inserts the two remaining trays. He rotates the furniture regularly. The student assembles the top tray in the middle and then disassembles it from the side bars before putting it back in place. Finally, the student attaches the wheels.
